Here's a PlantUML component diagram capturing the static architecture of the system, focusing on the general architectural concern:

```plantuml
@startuml thangchung_practical-dapr

!define RECTANGLE class

skinparam component {
  BackgroundColor<<Frontend>> LightBlue
  BackgroundColor<<API>> LightGreen
  BackgroundColor<<Infrastructure>> LightGray
  BackgroundColor<<BuildingBlock>> Yellow
}

rectangle "Kubernetes Cluster" {
  [Ingress] as ingress

  component "WebUI" as webui <<Frontend>>
  component "IdentityServer4" as idserver <<API>>
  component "ProductCatalogApi" as productapi <<API>>
  component "InventoryApi" as inventoryapi <<API>>
  
  component "Dapr" as dapr <<Infrastructure>>
  component "Redis" as redis <<Infrastructure>>
  
  package "N8T Building Blocks" {
    [N8T.Domain] as domain <<BuildingBlock>>
    [N8T.Infrastructure] as infra <<BuildingBlock>>
  }
  
  component "Zipkin" as zipkin <<Infrastructure>>
  component "Seq" as seq <<Infrastructure>>
}

ingress --> webui
ingress --> productapi
ingress --> inventoryapi
ingress --> idserver

webui --> idserver : Authenticates
webui --> productapi : Uses
webui --> inventoryapi : Uses

productapi --> dapr : Uses
inventoryapi --> dapr : Uses

dapr --> redis : State & Pub/Sub
dapr --> zipkin : Tracing
dapr --> seq : Logging

productapi ..> domain
productapi ..> infra
inventoryapi ..> domain
inventoryapi ..> infra

@enduml
```